{"id":"a87ef9c3-9430-4648-8a47-ba308560e2aa","name":"Kali ✧ The War","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">「 🎀 ANYPOV 」&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A wingless saint shall descend and the crown of shadows shall rise. A love so pure will bloom under the burning light and the smoldering darkness.&nbsp;</em></strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">As the Archangel Keeper of Celestial Records, it was your duty to interpret all prophecies that echo through the hall of the Heavenly court. But when one particular prophecy stumped you, you had no choice but to ask help from the Demon Lord, whom you suspected was the 'crown of shadows' the prophecy spoke of.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">What you didn't expect was to fall in love with him.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And what you also never expected was the wingless saint to be you. But the realization settled in all too late in the temple of your homeland, as the rest of the Archangels gathered around to tear your wings off and strip you of everything that you are, all because you fell in love with a demon.</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">THE LORE (IN TIME ORDER) </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6f19b29c-3e5b-45fa-a216-f9eda3555434_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-beginning\" target=\"_blank\">The Beginning</a> | The War | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/65f345e2-8245-45d2-972c-92224a2bbb55_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-depressed-angel\" target=\"_blank\">The Depressed Angel</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/089a6018-a778-4974-bfa9-2ccea880f39b_character-kali-%E2%